{"tid":358280,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【亞視永恒】穆桂英大破天門陣","createTime":"2017-08-13T15:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T09:03:50.000Z","uid":130591,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40ed5a33f4fd36a0206f235b33e61dd4d62d40da","tid":358280,"uid":130591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:22:59.000Z","msg":"今日偶爾一開MyTV，見到大台又放多左亞視劇集<br />\n竟然有《穆桂英》，我當堂嚇左一跳<br />\n連追五集<br />\n發覺10幾年亞視嘅古裝片製作已超越了大台現在嘅水準<br />\n取材、節奏、對白、演技、陣容、鏡頭 都係大台難以企及<br />\n尤其係演員嘅對白，語言、語調都十足古人，好古雅，當然有輕鬆搞笑，都係根據人物設定<br />\n楊門女將嘅陣容，相信今日大台都搵唔返。<br />\n<br />\n 總結：In ATV we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50526db66a2bc543698efd4849c6b7da6083544a","tid":358280,"uid":130591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T02:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0b2d572ce19ebc5b69ff76f5c415180b1ffa95","tid":358280,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T03:06:49.000Z","msg":"呢套野煎Pan好似有份做2打6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e3d4a3997670ecd99cf7083363147f352c3b1f","tid":358280,"uid":26451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T03:09:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79ae0b5c373e51d6c57bc6a52558acea26378989","tid":358280,"uid":130591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T16:52:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢套野煎Pan好似有份做2打6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇留意<br />\n<br />\n但睇完之後㩒返出去剛好播緊《踩過界》<br />\n見到林韋辰條頸嘅乾癯，同十幾年前做耶律皓南時嘅靚仔樣<br />\n真係不勝感慨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8782783038dfd319a5514bf5773e05d2bec21d95","tid":358280,"uid":130591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c